    <div class="main review-item" id="7422437">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7422437/" class="title-link">《反景入森林：人类学的观照、理论与实践》（1）</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7422437"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/83416338/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u83416338-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/83416338/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">猎户豆豆</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-03-23"
      class="main-meta">2015-03-23 15:36:01</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7422437_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这似乎是一本关于人类学的教材，但却是一本导论部分就看的我热血沸腾的书。所以在接下来的几周里想专门就此书写点感想，做些笔记。 之所以说看导论部分看的热血沸腾是因为作者的文字充满着个人的经历，而这些个人的经历与思考也与自己的经历以及现在所思所考的东西有着高度的吻...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7422437_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7422437_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





